b"With these keys in their heads, this march on the pitch, Pioli's Milan is ready to give themselves a long life, supported by the renewals of the pieces that, with the Emilian coach, have grown and enhanced.\nAfter Calabria, Saelemaekers & Kjaer, Maldini & Massara are working on\n4/"

b"Kjaer is among the symbols and the first architects of Pioli's Milan, able to technically grow hand in hand with the team and to bring a winning mentality to the locker room, day after day and match after match. This spirit is then clearly visible on the field.\n2/"
